      "details": {
        "title": "Red Snow",
        "description": "\n 1st place winner of the 2023 Bigmode Game Jam!\nRED SNOW is being revamped for a Steam release! Wishlist it today!\nFollow Red Snow development on twitter, @playRedSnow\nGet ready for RED SNOW, a dynamic downhill winter sports game created in just 2 1/2 weeks for the Big Mode 2023 Game Jam! \nDive into intense and exciting downhill gameplay across a variety of winter-sports modes. Challenge players worldwide for a chance to claim your spot on the leaderboard!\nLaggy? Try enabling \"Use hardware acceleration when available\" In Chrome Settings -> System.\n\n~~LORE~~\nThe year is 2146. The battle for freedom intensifies as communist invaders target America's pristine ski slopes. In Aspen, Colorado, a lone American patriot and winter sports enthusiast named JOHN CLOD takes a defiant stand against an army of communist ski jumpers.\n Welcome to RED SNOW.\nBy\n \n@CharlieBratches - Lead programmer, voice acting, maestro\n\n    \n@BaseMaterial - Artistic genius\n    \n@LyerionClash - Programming, audio FX\n\n\n    @tkinthepocket - Original music\n\n",
